title: UC LAUNCH Demo Day
description: Over the past five years, LAUNCH's alumni have raised over $125 million, topped the Forbes 30 under 30 list! Whether you are an investor, an entrepreneur, a student, or a community leader,  you cannot miss this event! 10 new innovative startups have worked through the 12 weeks of LAUNCH Spring Cohort to be the finalists. Register to check them out!
